Task 1

	use sniffex.c directly. with empty filter


Task 2

	• Capture the ICMP packets between two specific hosts (i.e. given IP addresses).


	use	(icmp and (src host 10.0.2.5 and dst host 10.0.2.4) or (src host 10.0.2.4 and dst host 10.0.2.5))
	as filter expression.

	• Capture the TCP packets that have a destination port range from 10 to 100.

	use (tcp dst portrange 10-100) as filter


Task 3

	use sniffexPass.c It will print entered password to password.txt

